<p>I'm not going to hazard a guess as to the origin of "group mind", but the idea of the "group mind" becoming stronger and/or more intelligent with more individuals in physical proximity seems to flow naturally from it. I can promise that Mass Effect (or any other video game) did not originate the concept.</p>
